Package com.cloudpos

Provides the basic interface and class for the devices.

See: Description

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    AlgorithmConstants
    This interface contains a number of useful constants for use with methods that accept a algorithm as a parameter.
    Device
    The Device interface is the root for all device interfaces.
    DeviceSpec
    device specification.
    OperationListener
    The listener of asynchronous method.
    OperationResult
    Operation results are generated by a device implementation to notify the application of the completion of a requested operation.
    TerminalSpec
    Provides terminal specification.
    TimeConstants
    This interface contains a number of useful constants for use with methods that accept a timeout as a parameter.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    POSTerminal
    POSTerminal is a manager to get all the device objects.
  • Exception Summary 
    Exception Description
    DeviceException
    An DeviceException is thrown when access problems are detected by the service controls.
